01:36:22.149 --> 01:36:23.951
<i>of microbial predator</i>
<i>on Adrian.</i>

1527
01:36:24.018 --> 01:36:26.120
<i>it'll be in the clouds</i>
<i>where Astrophage breeds.</i>

1528
01:36:26.186 --> 01:36:28.055
