2148
02:25:19.588 --> 02:25:21.889
[music swells]

2149
02:25:29.598 --> 02:25:31.332
[Rocky chittering]

2150
02:25:35.803 --> 02:25:38.339
[chittering]

2151
02:25:39.240 --> 02:25:40.941
I'm here. buddy.

2152
02:25:41.008 --> 02:25:43.310
[music crescendoes]

2153
02:26:03.665 --> 02:26:05.533
[Grace] <i>Earth. Rocky.</i>

2154
02:26:05.600 --> 02:26:07.134
<i>Rocky. Earth.</i>

2155
02:26:07.201 --> 02:26:09.903
<i>Hello. Earth. I am Rocky.</i>

2156
02:26:09.970 --> 02:26:11.573
<i>I am Rocky from Erid.</i>

2157
02:26:11.640 --> 02:26:14.308
<i>I am not Rocky from movie.</i>
<i>No. no. no. no.</i>

2158
02:26:14.375 --> 02:26:16.343
[Grace]
<i>I'm pretty sure they know that.</i>

2159
02:26:16.410 --> 02:26:18.879
<i>I've left you detailed logs</i>
<i>of all of our findings</i>

2160
02:26:18.946 --> 02:26:22.883
<i>and I threw in a little</i>
<i>something else just for fun.</i>

2161
02:26:24.818 --> 02:26:27.454
<i>Hopefully it all makes sense.</i>

2162
02:26:27.522 --> 02:26:28.757
<i>And if not</i>

2163
02:26:28.822 --> 02:26:30.457
<i>You're smart.</i>

2164
02:26:31.025 --> 02:26:32.493
<i>You'll figure it out.</i>

2165
02:26:34.094 --> 02:26:36.598
<i>This is</i>
<i>Dr. Captain Ryland Grace</i>

2166
02:26:36.665 --> 02:26:38.098
<i>reporting from the</i> Hail Mary.

2167
02:26:38.165 --> 02:26:40.367
<i>As the Eridians say</i>

2168
02:26:42.737 --> 02:26:45.272
[upbeat rock music playing]

2169
02:26:57.051 --> 02:26:58.419
Let's begin.

2170
02:27:30.351 --> 02:27:31.786
[music ends]

2171
02:27:31.852 --> 02:27:34.888
